Runs the app in development mode : 
  npm start
  Open http://localhost:3000 to view it in the browser.

start server : 
  cd /var/www/html/react/webpack/facebook-create-react-app/my-app/src
  sudo nohup node server.js &

stop server : 
  ps aux | grep node
  sudo kill -9 PID

deploy client : 
  npm run build
  upload "build" folder to /var/www/html/react/webpack/facebook-create-react-app/my-app/


Reference : https://github.com/facebookincubator/create-react-app
            https://github.com/facebookincubator/create-react-app/blob/master/packages/react-scripts/template/README.md
            